Package: gnome-shell-extension-obision-one-win
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         gnome-shell (>= 48)
Description: Stage Manager-style window management for GNOME Shell
 Obision One Win is a GNOME Shell extension that provides
 Stage Manager-style window management with live thumbnail previews.
 .
 Features:
  - Stage Manager mode with side panel
  - Live thumbnails of inactive windows
  - Real-time window clones
  - Quick window switching
  - Customizable panel width and position
  - Auto-minimize inactive windows
  - Theme integration with GNOME accent colors
